    "description": {
      "value": "<p>If you have the @UUID[Compendium.starfinder-field-test-for-pf2e.sf2e-feats.Item.zsXV8mcHVZqx6FVj]{Critical Explosion} feat and plant a mine, you can choose to deal a different type of damage depending on your choice of discipline.</p><p>If you have the @UUID[Compendium.starfinder-field-test-for-pf2e.sf2e-feats.Item.JoA3Q3W5a70g3aZV]{Explosive Shot} feat, when you Modify a weapon with Explosive Shot, you can choose the splash damage dealt to be a different type of damage depending on your choice of discipline.</p><p>Biotech deals acid damage, magitech deals force damage, and necrotech deals void damage.</p>",
